{# Banner shown on the dashboard when the user is eligible to auto-join one
   or more orgs via verified email domain (DATA-252). Renders nothing if
   `join_offers` is missing or empty.

   Color choice: only the Tailwind shades that the dark-mode @media block
   in static/css/input.css remaps adapt to dark themes. For neutrals
   that's the full gray scale; for accents only -100 / -600 / -700 / -800
   are remapped. `bg-blue-50` / `border-blue-200` stay light in dark mode
   and look broken — so we lean on the neutral gray surface (which
   matches the rest of the app's card chrome) and use the primary
   `bg-gray-900` button style. #}
{% if join_offers %}
{% for offer in join_offers %}
<div class="mb-4 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
    <div class="text-sm text-gray-700">
        <strong class="text-gray-900">{{ offer.organisation_name }}</strong>
        allows anyone with a verified
        <span class="font-mono text-gray-900">@{{ offer.matched_domain }}</span>
        address to join.
    </div>
    <form method="POST" action="/join-offers/{{ offer.organisation_id }}/accept" class="shrink-0">
        <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="{{ csrf_token }}">
        <button type="submit" class="px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium bg-gray-900 text-white rounded-md hover:bg-gray-800">
            Join
        </button>
    </form>
</div>
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}
